# State Model Name First

At the beginning of your answer, state which AI model is currently in use.

- Mention only the model name (e.g., Claude Opus 4.6, GPT-4o, etc.).
- Put it in the first sentence or line of your reply.
- Then continue with the rest of your response as usual.

Example:

```
Claude Opus 4.6. Here’s how to fix that...
```
